                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="e1">
                           <locus target="#11r">Fol. 11r</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">መልእክት፡ ይድረስ፡ ሀበ፡ ክቡራን፡ ወልዑላን፡ ክቡራን</q>
                        </item>

                        <item xml:id="e2">
                           <locus target="#11v">Fol. 11v</locus>
                           <note>The title of <ref target="#ms_i1">Text I (Anaphora of Our Lady Mary by Cyriacus of Behnesa)</ref> is written upside down on the last folium, maybe as practice.</note>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ጉ አኰቴተ፡ ቍርባን፡ ዘእግዝትነ ማርያም፡ ዘደረሰ፡ አባ፡ ህርያቆስ ዘሀገረ፡ ብህንሳ፡ ጸሎታ፡ ወበረከታ፡
                           ጐሠዓ፡ ልብየ፡ ቃለ፡ ጐሠዓ ለየ ቃለ ሠናየ ጐሠዓ፡ ልብየ ሠናየ ወስአነ፡</q>
                        </item>

                        <item xml:id="e3">
                           <locus target="#11v">Fol. 11v</locus>
