                    <locus target="#11r">fol. 11r</locus>.
                    <hi rendition="simple:smallcaps">MSS</hi> <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/DSEthiop17">DS Ethiop. 17</ref>,
                    <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/DSEthiop20">DS Ethiop. 20</ref> and
                    <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/DSEthiop24">DS Ethiop. 24</ref>
                   belong together as parts of an unfinished manuscript begun in
                   <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC2804Egypt">Egypt</placeName>. See the description
                    and the dating of <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/DSEthiop20"><hi rendition="simple:smallcaps">MS</hi> DS Ethiop. 20</ref>.
